{"tid":1961201,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"當法律內容同檢控權都喺「敵人」手上嘅時候，係冇人可以幫到我地","createTime":"2020-04-06T15:24:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-12T13:48:04.000Z","uid":41355,"like":28,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"58b888983b65613673dbaf3a9dc3572e99400cc4","tid":1961201,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T15:24:43.000Z","msg":"近日由於警察同律政司努力進行清算工作，好多人忽然明白原來司法制度唔係「有險可守」。不過，大家係咁講「法治已死」令我有少少擔心，大家係咪仲覺得法治曾經存在過？係咪覺得司法真係應該保障到大家？<br />\n<br />\n要知道香港以前嘅情況「冇咁差」係因為以前嘅政府對抗爭(或扮抗爭)者網開一面。重要嘢要重覆一次：<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">以前政府其實係處處手下留情</span></strong>。所以張曉明嗰句「你們不是好好活著嗎？」絕對係冇講錯，係一個 inconvenient truth 嚟。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">香港法律執正嚟做係可以好嚴苛嘅，少少行差踏錯都可能犯法。只要案件去到法官面前，佢就有責任「秉公」審理。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n法庭從來唔係用嚟處理政治問題嘅地方，但唔知點解香港人卻覺得法官無所不能。去到最後司法仍然係「三權」其中一支，本質上仍然係幫政權施政嘅一個機構。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">因為缺乏民主制度而寄望司法可以幫你取得「公義」其實係一個幾 on9 嘅諗法嚟。</span></strong>可能係因為香港泛民主派律師多，佢哋日日幫司法機構洗白，所以俾咗公眾一個錯誤印像。事實上普通法嘅法官本質係因循同保守嘅，只不過喺一個「不作為」嘅政府襯托之下，喺某啲時候會好似比較進取而已。<br />\n<br />\n聽落我好似為班法官辯護咁，但其實我講咁多嘢係想大家明白，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">當法律內容同檢控權都喺「敵人」手上嘅時候，係冇人可以幫到你嘅。</span></strong>重一女田嘢又重覆一次：當法律內容同檢控權都喺「敵人」手上嘅時候，係冇人可以幫到你嘅。<br />\n<br />\n呢幾年累積落嚟一大堆「不公義」嘅官司仍然要打，但唔好搞錯，官司絕對唔應該係「主戰場」所在。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大家要認清問題唔在於某幾個法官身上 (雖然有啲官的確係比較__)，更加唔係法律嘅解釋(interpretation)，而係法律嘅實際內容同埋對執法者嘅管制。 </span></strong>(申延閱讀： <a href=\"https://www.vjmedia.com.hk/articles/2016/07/25/138879\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vjmedia.com.hk%2Farticles%2F2016%2F07%2F25%2F138879&d=oVNa%2F3rGcR5VJv77DJ2lewbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=212fef6f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.vjmedia.com.hk/articles/2016/07/25/138879</a> )<br />\n<br />\n呢幾年本土思潮崛起，但香港人仍然唔習慣 #光復自己，好多時遇到困難只會更依賴權威。究竟香港人眼中一個理想嘅香港係點嘅呢？呢種討論坊間少之又少。變咗香港人只能夠被動咁嘗試抵抗政治嘅衰敗，但冇任何得到大眾普遍認可往前進嘅方向。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大家識得講「法治已死」，但知唔知道自己所嚮往嘅司法制度係點呢？</span></strong> （唔通真係「黃絲就無罪」？如果係咁我第一個潛逃返大陸，人民法院萬歲。）我敢斷言，未構築到理想世界之前，香港嘅抗爭運動係唔會成功嘅。唔好以為識得講句「法治已死」好叻豬，仲停留喺恥笑楊岳橋嘅水平，你能夠打倒嘅，*最多*只係楊岳橋本身。（同埋到九月佢咪又會高票當選⋯ 你估啲黃絲真係有腦架咩）"},{"pid":"4321e72eea2c45ccd25cac50db99e89d1a50cd95","tid":1961201,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T15:26:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hnfong/posts/916173641877\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhnfong%2Fposts%2F916173641877&d=oVNa%2F3rGcR5VJv77DJ2lewbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=47974573\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hnfong/posts/916173641877</a>"},{"pid":"abbe8ad13401217cb3b1f9a4c7579bc768278e1c","tid":1961201,"uid":258578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T15:27:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"be8d744cfb9dc6e691b5a62ae95b10d91772affc","tid":1961201,"uid":258578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T15:28:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1f74d0947efc18e8deefb4cf0fa52f3e6c31cd14","tid":1961201,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T15:32:59.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"e2b12e6def9e6ce7b912eaa7eb60a15c24049c91","tid":1961201,"uid":83228,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T15:37:16.000Z","msg":"首先 用字好重要 <br />\n呢啲唔係執正黎做 以前唔係網開一面<br />\n係rule of law 同rule by law的分別<br />\n依家已經係軍政府"},{"pid":"a7c6f33492d899e3d70f19e29a31215e7bd9ce71","tid":1961201,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T15:37:18.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"ff808e1966f526cf87f48d54f622c24bd99e0592","tid":1961201,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T15:41:02.000Z","msg":"我期望香港可以有一個普通法制度。法官由民選總統委任，終身擔任。<br />\n<br />\n香港人不分黃藍，只要未至於動武，都可以暢所欲言，無需畏懼當權者嘅恐嚇；受武力攻擊也可以自衛。<br />\n<br />\n當然，我地都可以為自己選擇人間地獄嘅，以下是一個革命政權的做法：<br />\n唯求歷史不要重複<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1961142/page/1#preview\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1961142/page/1#preview</a>"},{"pid":"c4f2fba766780b01cbcdb0bc54a2c07ad2d85172","tid":1961201,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff808e1966f526cf87f48d54f622c24bd99e0592","tid":1961201,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T15:41:02.000Z","msg":"我期望香港可以有一個普通法制度。法官由民選總統委任，終身擔任。<br />\n<br />\n香港人不分黃藍，只要未至於動武，都可以暢所欲言，無需畏懼當權者嘅恐嚇；受武力攻擊也可以自衛。<br />\n<br />\n當然，我地都可以為自己選擇人間地獄嘅，以下是一個革命政權的做法：<br />\n唯求歷史不要重複<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1961142/page/1#preview\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1961142/page/1#preview</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T16:07:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c9be38fb0f2fb933b7b28ff817b208ec1e2a0cd1","tid":1961201,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T16:08:59.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"09a73932b056a0c3fa8dce6224d84088033f67b6","tid":1961201,"uid":120123,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T16:10:29.000Z","msg":"禮崩樂壞，當法律制裁唔到班冚家鏟的時候，就要私了。"},{"pid":"03f7739cb1e8563561a1f484874e9c27adc922e4","tid":1961201,"uid":41355,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"09a73932b056a0c3fa8dce6224d84088033f67b6","tid":1961201,"uid":120123,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T16:10:29.000Z","msg":"禮崩樂壞，當法律制裁唔到班冚家鏟的時候，就要私了。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T16:24:22.000Z","msg":"無可否認<br />\n似乎呢個係唯一得到公義既方法"},{"pid":"9e361fd1c7f13e9625bb5bb8c00f6c7aecac1b36","tid":1961201,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T16:28:34.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"60074c75c32003ed1a0802ff996e4f256c98ee50","tid":1961201,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T16:43:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"373b68dbab4173dcd5c7dee91c1341c129519fa5","tid":1961201,"uid":350350,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T17:29:44.000Z","msg":"香港而家嘅問題係制度嚴重腐敗<br />\n而法律係用嚟維持制度穩定<br />\n<strong>所以而家香港法律就係維持𡁵一個腐爛嘅制度運作暢順</strong><br />\n<br />\n奴隸覺得唔公平係冇問題<br />\n只要社會仲運作𡁵，政府就有錢收<br />\n<br />\n<strong>法官同黑狗都係請返嚟保持制度運作<br />\n本質係冇唔同</strong><br />\n<br />\n香港人一日未夠決心推翻制度，一日都贏唔到<br />\n決心唔係講𡁵勇武做到幾多<br />\n<strong>勇武做更多都唔能夠carry全個社會</strong><br />\n<br />\n一兩個人犧牲自己，但多數人無動於衷<br />\n<strong>加埋嘅共業就係全部人都會輸到入集中營</strong>"},{"pid":"a835a724e51c0aa06a073737287ff37d50c2f7f6","tid":1961201,"uid":182860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T18:47:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dae27153037834d47898781bca1ffd37d04cec3c","tid":1961201,"uid":182860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T18:47:56.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c7d951decc7a9775cf1be278d2af4f66f9fd1825","tid":1961201,"uid":182860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T18:48:53.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"43beddcf6f57323b9884f1dcc5ca555e5c542194","tid":1961201,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"03f7739cb1e8563561a1f484874e9c27adc922e4","tid":1961201,"uid":41355,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"09a73932b056a0c3fa8dce6224d84088033f67b6","tid":1961201,"uid":120123,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T16:10:29.000Z","msg":"禮崩樂壞，當法律制裁唔到班冚家鏟的時候，就要私了。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T16:24:22.000Z","msg":"無可否認<br />\n似乎呢個係唯一得到公義既方法"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T18:57:21.000Z","msg":"係呢一刻來臨之前我地都要用盡力量減輕警法勾結既傷害<br />\n<br />\n唔係話要全靠正當武力私了<br />\n<br />\n起碼登記做陪審團同埋唔做立會白兵"},{"pid":"9241edf801c9c832500fe159b2c79b1003735acc","tid":1961201,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T19:00:10.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">警法相衛<br />\n警法勾結<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n呢D字要變成日常用語"},{"pid":"cf46912e20820a5fe52b1e859aa8542f79a86d82","tid":1961201,"uid":227650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T19:02:30.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"9c0c4425b8bae98158bbd318d207c422a551e484","tid":1961201,"uid":235588,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T19:10:56.000Z","msg":"其實有無諗過係法律本身存廢嘅問題？eg暴動、煽動呢類係咪過時？ 襲警有無灰色地帶，有無偏離大家所理解嘅「襲擊」？ 個波好不幸地應該要拋比行政提出修例，再由立法會審議。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而香港英式法治，個人認為本質上無咩太大改變。（唔識評價本質是好是壞）"},{"pid":"96e67bce925634cfdc99d8304b941ff782be8f32","tid":1961201,"uid":267909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e2b12e6def9e6ce7b912eaa7eb60a15c24049c91","tid":1961201,"uid":83228,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T15:37:16.000Z","msg":"首先 用字好重要 <br />\n呢啲唔係執正黎做 以前唔係網開一面<br />\n係rule of law 同rule by law的分別<br />\n依家已經係軍政府"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T19:19:23.000Z","msg":"依家衰到連 rule by law 都係<br />\n直接軍政府<br />\npopo is the law"},{"pid":"9160527b15a3319889b8bd64e12a5a2fecdf08ef","tid":1961201,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T01:46:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"53e3c24cd026d6731baf7583f727fb57345421fe","tid":1961201,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T13:26:34.000Z","msg":"PUSH"}],"pinned":{"pid":"3170d5bf1da257b758e2df0141f51a57acaad8ef","tid":1961201,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T13:34:50.000Z","msg":"今日緊急法判案再次證明，唔駛對zombie有任何幻想"}}